{
  "stem": "2713.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If you survive, you'll have it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He didn't want to take it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But then I begged him, because I knew I'm going to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't believe in what he's saying to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I said, you have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he took it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, I give it to you back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You will see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I gave him the ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were waiting there for hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we begged them-- we ask the Germans, what-- what's happening?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They told us, it won't be too long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we found out-- I don't know, look, if it's true or not, but it's what we were told-- that two days before, 2,000 Romanian girls came, and they were all gassed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's why we are waiting, because they have to dispose the bodies so we can go in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we definitely knew that we're going to be finished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "While we were waiting people were still dropping dead, so they had less then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Then in middle of the night, an order came that we're all going in to have a shower.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't believe them, because we knew this is what they say usually when people are going to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't believe them that we're going to have a shower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we went to have a shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They asked us to be undressed, and I went into the shower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The only thing you can leave-- if you have a belt with you, you can hold your belt on you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- we didn't know what the belt is for or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What do you need a belt for?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You haven't got any clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What do you need a belt for?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we went in to have the shower.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
